Barbara Everest https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barbara_Everest 0 Barbara Everest (19 June 1890 – 9 February 1968) was a British stage and film actress. She was born in Southfields, Surrey, and made her screen debut in the 1916 film The Man Without a Soul. Barbara_Everest ( 19_June_1890 – 9_February_1968 ) was a_British_stage_and_film_actress .
